OL,3,CParents who suffer death of a child
OL,4,Cgiven right to compassionate leave
OL,6,FA new law has been established in
OL,7,Fwhich will provide parents who have
OL,8,Fsuffered the death of a child access
OL,9,Fto compassionate leave and financial
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FThe Social Security Minister, Deputy
OL,13,FLyndsay Feltham, has updated the
OL,14,Fisland's employment legislation to
OL,15,Fgive working parents who have lost a
OL,16,Fchild under the age of 18, including
OL,17,Fstillbirths, the right to two weeks of
OL,18,Funpaid leave.
